<EventsDetail ID="x62897" Name="Application" Layout="general_activities.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Event Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Apply for Graduation</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">How to Apply for Graduation</Abstract><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Event Details" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>Applying&nbsp;to&nbsp;graduate from BYU-Idaho can be done in a matter of minutes using the online application.&nbsp; To apply, simply log on to&nbsp;your <a href="https://my.byui.edu">my.byui.edu</a> student account, select the "Student" tab, and search for "Graduation Application" at the bottom of the gray links on the left side of the page.</p>
<br />
<p>The online application will walk you through a step-by-step process.&nbsp; Once your application is submitted, you can then return to the application page to review the current status of your application.&nbsp; The application deadlines are also displayed on the application.</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</p>
